    </layer>
    <layer level="2" name="Layer 2">
      <focus/>
      <content>IR Lifecycle integration (Detect → Contain in Respond phase); Relationships: Precedes eradication/recovery; Links to MTTD (earlier metric), influences MTTR.</content>
    </layer>
    <layer level="3" name="Layer 3">
      <focus/>
      <content>Formula: MTTC = Σ(Containment Time - Detection Time) / # Incidents; Steps: Log timestamps, aggregate data, compute average; Tools: SIEM, ticketing systems.</content>
    </layer>
    <layer level="4" name="Layer 4">
      <focus/>
